              <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/all-hotels-san-jose\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in San Jose.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4>Where to stay in San Jose<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The neighborhood of Am&#xF3;n in San Jose has some nice buildings to see and restaurants to visit, like Cafe Rojo and De Ac&#xE1;.  <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/san-jose-casa-69\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Casa 69\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/06150209\/220427216-450x338.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Casa 69<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hostel-finca-escalante-san-jose\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Escalanta Hostel\" height=\"300\" width=\"4