interest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/22145457\/costa-rica-3-week-itinerary-4-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/22145457\/costa-rica-3-week-itinerary-4-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3-Week Itinerary: The Complete Travel Guide\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<p>Please note that you can only enter Tortuguero national park by boat or light aircraft. You&#x2019;ll need to drive to La Pavona, where you can park your car in a guarded place for 10 USD per day. From here, jump on a boat and sail an hour along the river, spotting caymans and crocodiles!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12200050\/tortuguero-24.jpg\" alt=\"boat tortuguero costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"323\" alt=\"boat tortuguero costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-75693 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" dat