guero-21-600x403.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12181546\/Tortuguero-21-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/12181546\/Tortuguero-21.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The primary hatching season is July to October, but there are plenty of other things to see and do in Tortuguero outside of these months. One of the main activities is a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tortu-night-walk\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">night walk in the Tortuguero Nature Reserve<\/a>, where a guide will take you by boat into the depths of the rainforest. Under the cover of darkness, you&#x2019;ll be able to see rare and beautiful wildlife, like the red-eyed tree frog.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/tortuguero\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Read everything about Tortuguero National Park<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\