 a 4&#xD7;4 or any clearance from the ground. We recommend <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">renting a car<\/a> if you can, as once you&#x2019;re in La Fortuna, there aren&#x2019;t many transport options and the sights are very remote.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8.jpg\" alt=\"road trip Costa Rica 3 week itinerary \"><\/noscript><img width=\"267\" height=\"338\" alt=\"road trip Costa Rica 3 week itinerary \" class=\"wp-image-78865 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1515px) 100vw, 1515px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8.jpg 1515w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-473x600.jpg 473w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-639x810.jpg 639w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-267x338.jpg 267w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-129x163.jpg 129w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-142x180.jpg 142w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-606x768.jpg 606w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-808x1024.jpg 808w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143806\/camping-costa-rica-8-852x1080.jpg 852w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/w