https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tabacon-cr\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tabacon Resort<\/a>. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/lafortuna-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here are all your hotel options<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/lafortuna-casaluna\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Casa Luna Hotel &amp; Spa\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16170817\/293205329-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Casa Luna Hotel &amp; Spa<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/lafortuna-sangregado\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Sangregado Lodge\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16170825\/315393961-450x338.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Sangregado Lodge<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-day-9-of-your-3-weeks-in-costa-rica-la-fortuna\">Day 9 of your 3 weeks in Costa Rica: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/la-fortuna\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">La Fortuna<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Enjoy your first full day in La Fortuna, a stunning natural area home to the Arenal Volcano, geothermal springs, and the famous Mistico Hanging Bridges. There are many hikes to enjoy in the Arenal National Park, so choose from one of the many trails that hug the volcano. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162713\/la-fortuna-4.jpg\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary la fortuna Mistico Arenal Hanging Bridges\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary la fortuna Mistico Arenal Hanging Bridges\" class=\"wp-image-73884 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162713\/la-fortuna-4.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162713\/la-fortuna-4-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162713\/la-fortuna-4-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162713\/la-fortuna-4-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162713\/la-fortuna-4-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162713\/la-fortuna-4-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\