\">\n<h3 id=\"h-day-10-la-fortuna-to-monteverde\">Day 10: La Fortuna to Monteverde<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This might just be one of the best journeys on your whole Costa Rica 3-week itinerary! Discover an extraordinary road that circles around the great Arenal Lake&#x2014;sitting in the shadow of the volcano&#x2014;and ends in green and luscious Monteverde.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4.jpg\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary hanging bridges costa rica la fortuna\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary hanging bridges costa rica la fortuna\" class=\"wp-image-73894 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-600x899.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170835\/la-fortuna-Mistico-4.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>On your way, stop at Mistico Hanging Bridges, which are about a 30-minutes drive from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/la-fortuna\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">La Fortuna<\/a>. These adrenaline-pumping bridges stand at the height of 45 meters above the rainforest, giving you unparalleled views over the rainforest treetops, the volcano, and the opportunity to spot some elusive Costa Rican wildlife.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Visit the majestic <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/rio-celeste-waterfalls\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rio Celeste Waterfalls<\/a> which is a small detour on the way from La Fortuna to Monteverde. Please note that road 143 from Lake Arenal towards <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/rio-celeste-waterfalls\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rio Celeste<\/a> is not good for car that are low to the ground.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173842\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-73916 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173842\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-1.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173842\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173842\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173842\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-1-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173842\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-1-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173842\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-1-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173842\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-1-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173842\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-1-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173842\/la-