ir.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173928\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-4.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-how-to-get-from-la-fortuna-to-monteverde\">How to get from La Fortuna to Monteverde<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>By Car:<\/strong>&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The drive from La Fortuna to Monteverde may seem close on the map, but it will take 3 hours because of Lake Arenal. The views are incredible though, so you won&#x2019;t want to rush this journey. Leave some time to take photos and stop at the Mistico Hanging Bridges!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The road is good all the way to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Monteverde<\/a>, so you won&#x2019;t need a 4&#xD7;4. However, you might want a car with a bit of clearance from the ground once you arrive in Monteverde, as the roads are older.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 3 week road trip\"><\/noscript><img width=\"251\" height=\"338\" alt=\"costa rica 3 week road trip\" class=\"wp-image-75256 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1428px) 100vw, 1428px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15.jpg 1428w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-446x600.jpg 446w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-602x810.jpg 602w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-251x338.jpg 251w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-121x163.jpg 121w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-134x180.jpg 134w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-571x768.jpg 571w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-762x1024.jpg 762w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-803x1080.jpg 803w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-1071x1440.jpg 1071w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-300x403.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-600x807.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03153310\/monteverde-costa-rica-15.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>By Bus or Shuttle:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Buses leave from La Fortuna to Monteverde, but they take around 7-8 hours and are not particularly comfortable. Alternatively, you could join a shared shuttle bus that is shorter and will pick you up from your hotel (cost around 50-60 USD). Many shuttles will include a boat ride across Arenal Lake as part of the transfer (see below).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Note:<\/strong> If you choose to travel by bus or shuttle, you won&#x2019;t have the flexibility of being able to visit the Mistico Hanging Bridges.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transport-lafortuna-monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book a bus or shuttle to Monteverde<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24170853\/la-fortuna-12.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-74412 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24170853\/la-fortuna-12.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24170853\/la-fortuna-12-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24170853\/la-fortuna-12-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24170853\/la-fortuna-12-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24170853\/la-fortuna-12-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24170853\/la-fortuna-12-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24170853\/la-fortuna-12-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24170853\/la-fortuna-12-512x768.jpg 512w, https: