-to-get-from-monteverde-to-santa-teresa\">How to get from Monteverde to Santa Teresa<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>By Car:<\/strong>&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Drive 1.5 hours south to the coastal town of Puntarenas. From here, go on the car ferry across the Gulf of Nicoya, which takes about 1 hour. You&#x2019;ll arrive in Paquera, and it takes another 1.5 hours to reach Santa Teresa. In total, it&#x2019;s about 4-5 hours to make the whole journey.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224631\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-14.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica ferry\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"costa rica ferry\" class=\"wp-image-74771 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224631\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-14.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224631\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-14-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224631\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-14-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224631\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-14-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224631\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-14-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224631\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-14-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224631\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-14-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224631\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224631\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-14-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.