r.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/30032453\/somos-450x253.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Somos<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/lua-villas-santa-teresa\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Lua Villas\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/30033312\/lua-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Lua Villas<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-day-13-15-santa-teresa\">Day 13 &#x2013; 15: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/santa-teresa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Santa Teresa<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>After your busy few weeks in the wilderness and nature of Costa Rica, relax and unwind for a few days in the coastal paradise of Santa Teresa. Here, your Costa Rican dreams come to life as you go galloping down open beaches on horseback, listen to live music around the campfire at night, and practice yoga on the beach. It&#x2019;s the perfect place to slow down, appreciate the ocean, and enjoy the bohemian vibes of the village.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/santa-teresa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">10 Best Things to do in Santa Teresa<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224733\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-20.jpg\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary santa teresa surfing\"><\/noscript><img width=\"232\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary santa teresa surfing\" class=\"wp-image-74785 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1317px) 100vw, 1317px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224733\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-20.jpg 1317w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224733\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-20-412x600.jpg 412w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224733\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-20-556x810.jpg 556w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26224733\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-20-232x338.jpg 232w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/