readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Read about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/best-beaches-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">the best beaches in Costa Rica<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05.jpg\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary Manuel Antonio Beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"246\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary Manuel Antonio Beach\" class=\"wp-image-72962 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1399px) 100vw, 1399px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05.jpg 1399w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-437x600.jpg 437w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-590x810.jpg 590w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-246x338.jpg 246w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-119x163.jpg 119w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-131x180.jpg 131w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-560x768.jpg 560w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-746x1024.jpg 746w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-787x1080.jpg 787w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-1049x1440.jpg 1049w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-300x412.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-600x823.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/07192520\/manuel-antonio-05.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-how-to-get-from-santa-teresa-to-manuel-antonio\">How to get from Santa Teresa to Manuel Antonio<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>By Car:<\/strong>&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The drive is around 6 hours (including the ferry from Paquera back to Puntarenas) on paved roads so you won&#x2019;t need a 4&#xD7;4. Break up the journey by making a quick stop at the famous<a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/pFnMvmiymcDAsgP5A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> Crocodile Bridge<\/a>, where you have a good chance of spotting crocodiles. However, please do not buy any meat from the sellers because this interferes with the crocodile&#x2019;s natural feeding habits. According to Costa Rican Law, <em>you are prohibited from feeding wildlife.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> &#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/wildlife-tourism\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Things to know about wildlife tourism<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143847\/camping-costa-rica-11.jpg\" alt=\"camping tips costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"239\" height=\"338\" alt=\"camping tips costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-78871 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143847\/camping-costa-rica-11.jpg 1360w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143847\/camping-costa-rica-11-425x600.jpg 425w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143847\/camping-costa-rica-11-574x810.jpg 574w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143847\/camping-costa-rica-11-239x338.jpg 239w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143847\/camping-costa-rica-11-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143847\/camping-costa-rica-11-115x163.jpg 115w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143847\/camping-costa-rica-11-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143847\/camping-costa-rica-11-544x768.jpg 544w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143847\/camping-costa-rica-11-725x1024.jpg 725w, https:\/\/static.