019;s so beautiful that many people buy a national park ticket just to visit for the day. Because these beaches are protected, they&#x2019;re pristine, with the whitest sand and bluest water. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6.jpg\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary manuel antonio Espadilla Beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary manuel antonio Espadilla Beach\" class=\"wp-image-72848 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/06185835\/manuel-antonio-6-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\