m\/costa-rica\/nauyaca-waterfalls\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nauyaca Waterfalls<\/a>. The entire journey from Manuel Antonio to Uvita takes 1 hour but add an extra 30 minutes to the trip to visit the waterfalls. Wander the trail to Nauyaca Waterfalls, where you&#x2019;ll find your very own jungle book scene! You can spend an afternoon here, looking at the two mighty falls and swimming in the natural pools below.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/22102519\/nauyaca-waterfall-costa-rica-1.jpg\" alt=\"nauyaca waterfall costa rica \"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"nauyaca waterfall costa rica \" class=\"wp-image-78744 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/22102519\/nauyaca-waterfall-costa-rica-1.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/22102519\/nauyaca-waterfall-costa-rica-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/22102519\/nauyaca-waterfall-costa-rica-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/22102519\/nauyaca-waterfall-costa-rica-1-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/22102519\/nauyaca-waterfall-costa-rica-1-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/22102519\/nauyaca-waterfall-costa-rica-1-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/22102519\/nauyaca-waterfall-costa-rica-1-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/22102519\/nauyaca-waterfall-costa-rica-1-512x768.jpg 512w, 