in=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/22102652\/nauyaca-waterfall-costa-rica-3.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-how-to-get-from-manuel-antonio-to-uvita\">How to get from Manuel Antonio to Uvita<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>By car:&#xA0;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The journey from Manuel Antonio to Uvita is very straightforward, directly on the highway and taking only 1-1.5 hours. However, if you want to visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/nauyaca-waterfalls\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nauyaca Waterfalls<\/a>, add an extra 30 minutes to your journey time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-72575 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/30180321\/uvita-30.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>By bus or shuttle:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#x2019;re traveling by public transport, you will not be able to make a stop at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/nauyaca-waterfalls\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nauyaca Waterfalls<\/a>. However, they are just a short journey from Uvita and can be visited on a day trip; plenty of tour companies leave from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/uvita\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Uvita<\/a> or Manuel Antonio for the falls.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Buses leave from Quepos (near Uvita) around 4 times a day and take approximately 2 hours, costing around 5 USD. You can take regular public buses to Quepos (from Manuel Antonio), which take about 30 minutes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10.jpg\" alt=\"travel guide Costa Rica 3 week itinerary road trip\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel guide Costa Rica 3 week itinerary road trip\" class=\"wp-image-72355 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-600x899.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26202022\/uvita-10.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A shuttle bus is a more comfortable option that allows you to be collected directly from your hotel in Manuel Antonio, saving you the trip to Quepos. It&#x2019;s a bit faster, taking 1.5 hours and costing around 40 USD per person.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/manuel-antonio\/uvita\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your shuttle bus here.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-where-to-stay-in-uvita\">Where to Stay in Uvita<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Uvita town is split up into two parts: the main town near the beach and the upper town across the highway toward Uvita Waterfall. When <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-uvita\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">staying in the main town<\/a>, hotels are more expensive, but you&#x2019;re always walking distance from the beach and mostly surrounded by lush greenery. Alternatively, camp at one of the nearby sites or go glamping!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotel-uvita-paradise\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Uvita Paradise\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/06143500\/293945169-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Uvita Paradise<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/uvita-karandi-hostel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Karandi Hostel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/06143448\/302014474-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Karandi Hostel<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-day-19-20-uvita\">Day 19 &#x2013; 20: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/uvita\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Uvita<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Uvita has it all: beautiful beaches with very few crowds, fantastic nature reserves, waterfalls, and amazing wildlife. It has a backpacker vibe that gives it a fun, youthful atmosphere (it also hosts a few festivals in the summer). <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201846\/uvita-2.jpg\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary uvita beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary uvita beach\" class=\"wp-image-72339 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201846\/uvita-2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201846\/uvita-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201846\/uvita-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201846\/uvita-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201846\/uvita-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201846\/uvita-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201846\/uvita-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201846\/uvita-2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201846\/uvita-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201846\/uvita-2-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/26201