it one more waterfall (like La Paz, which is an hour north of the city).<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>If you need a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/san-jose-airport-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hotel close to the airport<\/a>, stay at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/san-jose-airport-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Alajuela<\/a> instead of San Jose.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143926\/camping-costa-rica-14.jpg\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary sunset palm tree\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Costa Rica 3 week itinerary sunset palm tree\" class=\"wp-image-78877 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143926\/camping-costa-rica-14.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143926\/camping-costa-rica-14-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143926\/camping-costa-rica-14-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143926\/camping-costa-rica-14-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143926\/camping-costa-rica-14-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/22143926\/ca