ferred to as the &#x2018;Switzerland of Central America&#x2019;. &#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-expenses-for-a-costa-rica-3-week-itinerary\"><strong>Expenses for a Costa Rica 3-Week Itinerary<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A 3-week Costa Rica itinerary will cost you anywhere between 3000 &#x2013; 4000 USD. For example, this includes going out for lunch and dinner, accommodation, attraction tickets, and your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">rental car<\/a>. However, if you travel with two or more people, you can split accommodation and transport costs.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-budget\">\n        <span class=\"block-budget__title\">Budget<\/span><ul class=\"block-budget__list\"><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hotel: 50 &#x2013; 150 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hostel: 10 &#x2013; 180 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--restaurants\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Price per meal: 15 &#x2013; 30 USD\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Entrances: 125 &#x2013; 250 USD \/ week\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Transport: 600 &#x2013; 1000 USD \/ week\n                    <\/li><\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170805\/la-fortuna-Mistico-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-73890 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170805\/la-fortuna-Mistico-2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170805\/la-fortuna-Mistico-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170805\/la-fortuna-Mistico-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170805\/la-fortuna-Mistico-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170805\/la-fortuna-Mistico-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170805\/la-fortuna-Mistico-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170805\/la-fortuna-Mistico-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170805\