raw Colones from the ATM in Costa Rica or pay by card at most shops. Some restaurants charge USD by default, but it will significantly affect the total bill if you ask them to charge Colones. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transferwise\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Get a Wise card here; it&#x2019;s free!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103253\/how-to-move-abroad-transferwise.jpg\" alt=\"wise card\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"wise card\" class=\"wp-image-52991 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103253\/how-to-move-abroad-transferwise.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103253\/how-to-move-abroad-transferwise-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103253\/how-to-move-abroad-transferwise-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103253\/how-to-move-abroad-transferwise-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103253\/how-to-move-abroad-transferwise-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103253\/how-to-move-abroad-transferwise-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103253\/how-to-move-abroad-transferwise-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103253\/how-to-move-abroad-transferwise-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103253\/how-to-move-abroad-transferwise-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103253\/how-to