ltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-750x600.jpg 750w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-1013x810.jpg 1013w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-423x338.jpg 423w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-30x24.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-163x130.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-225x180.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-768x614.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-1350x1080.jpg 1350w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-1800x1440.jpg 1800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-300x240.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-600x480.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2-30x24.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/26033908\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The end of April to November is the rainy season, with the most rain in October. However, don&#x2019;t let this affect your choice as it never rains for long (only a few short rain showers each day). The rain also makes nature incredibly luscious! In addition, this period is much cheaper; you could even save a third of your total budget by traveling during this time.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/puerto-viejo\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Puerto Viejo<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/tortuguero\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tortuguero<\/a> are on the Caribbean coast and have slightly different seasons. August to October are generally dry, unlike other parts of Costa Rica.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"visa\">Do I Need a Visa for 3 Weeks in Costa Rica?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Most passport holders do not require a visa to enter Costa Rica. However, you will need a valid passport and an onward plane ticket to prove that you will exit Costa Rica within 90 days.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--visa \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--visa\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/get-visa-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Check here if you need a visa to enter<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-is-costa-rica-safe\">Is Costa Rica Safe?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Costa Rica is very safe for tourists, with some of the friendliest locals globally. It also has the lowest rate of violent crimes in Central America. However, like most countries in Latin America, it does have a few problems with drug trafficking, poverty, and pickpockets. Always keep your belongings within eyesight and exercise caution. This way, you&#x2019;re unlikely to experience any issues.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-safety\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tips on how to travel travel Safe<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/28193558\/santa-teresa-costa-rica-37-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"378\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-74966 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\