nside of the coconut too.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle.jpg\" alt=\"sustainable travel reusable water bottle\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"sustainable travel reusable water bottle\" class=\"wp-image-47339 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/reusable-water-bottle-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105541\/re